{"tid":493044,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 不獲《消費者報告》推介！原因竟然是....","createTime":"2017-12-08T06:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T08:40:10.000Z","uid":10958,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50e0ca17c0b7d58df414512584e1d171e261067f","tid":493044,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>iPhone X 不獲《消費者報告》推介！原因竟然是....</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1960000/1963900/cmsip_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1960000%2F1963900%2Fcmsip_1024.jpg&h=ed0d721e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone X 是 Apple 本年度最頂級的皇牌旗艦手機，更集 Apple 所有創新設計、技術於一身，iPhone X 本應可在各方面領先所有對手。不過，美國消費者權威機構《消費者報告》(Consumer Reports)，經過對 iPhone X 一連串測試後，最後竟指 iPhone X 雖然電池、鏡頭以及 Face ID 均為一流，但最終仍不及同廠的 iPhone 8。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>無法通過翻滾測試</strong><br />\n<br />\n《消費者報告》指出，iPhone X 不及同廠的 iPhone 8 的原因，是它無法通過佔分極高的翻滾測試，表示耐摔度不及 iPhone 8。《消費者報告》在測試中發現，iPhone X 使用了玻璃機身，進行滾動測試時 (見下影片)，出現機背玻璃跌爆、螢幕失靈等情況，相反 iPhone 8/8 Plus 卻可通過測試。《消費者報告》建議用家為 iPhone X 購買 AppleCare+ 和保護套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1960000/1963900/ip1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1960000%2F1963900%2Fip1_600.jpg&h=abc4f6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1960000/1963900/ip2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1960000%2F1963900%2Fip2_600.jpg&h=dc5a241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>相機功能出色</strong><br />\n<br />\n不過，《消費者報告》仍然讚賞 iPhone X 的新功能，特別是雙 OIS 鏡頭模組，令照片質素大幅提升，是為最佳的相機，領先排第二位的 iPhone 8。至於，電池測試方面，iPhone X 擁有 19.5 小時續航力，較 iPhone 8 多半小時，但與 Samsung Galaxy Note 8 的 26 小時相差甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GilmUD65BKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGilmUD65BKI&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d4554edc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GilmUD65BKI</a>"},{"pid":"de1a0546b004e39c0be60e5349fe3fc14fbd7992","tid":493044,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"iPhone X真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6621968a52d90985f8f711a67b46c3d900204a","tid":493044,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"即係叫你買配件就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c49d6f5dd9cfa27a4c1c31af7ac065b3add05ab","tid":493044,"uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩又一單遇冷就關機，可以順手開發埋發燒保護套同加熱ios"},{"pid":"ef287ddab492bdd6b828f567353258f20647c3ba","tid":493044,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"ip8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2157583d5fdab4d1804e27d288d8189f8c3a1b0","tid":493044,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"8plus is all-time king<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3adc780464f443e18ad36ffab5bb57f14266e9","tid":493044,"uid":17147,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"8 plus 轉 X, 但而家想轉返 8 plus. 主要覺得mon 太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e492e5a218fb84bc25cf2e734eff2784dfde988","tid":493044,"uid":3032,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1